Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们会遇到什么就行 告诉钴队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just tell 'em what they're walking into. Tell Cobalt.
