Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-从来就没打算  -你把她取出来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Was never intended-- - You took her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会授权银队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I cannot authorize Silver Team
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,执行战斗任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to perform combat operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该和我待在一起的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You should have stayed with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为庇护的交换\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}In exchange for asylum,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:01:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人要履行契约服务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}these persons submit to indentured service.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道怎么会这样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know how it happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其他家族 他们并不怕你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but the other families, they're not afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有你想要的东西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have something you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悬赏 凯瑟琳·哈尔西的位置\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A bounty, for Catherine Halsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know where she is.
