Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦066 你被捕了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren-066? You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪物唯一想让你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The only thing the monster wants
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道的是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}is for you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爱的所有一切\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that there's nothing you can ever love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它都可以夺走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that it can't take away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在信我了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You believe me now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两块抹茶饼干 两份澳洲坚果 两个酥饼\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Two matcha tea cookies, two macadamia nut, two shortbread--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一杯蓝油桃茶\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And a blue nectarine tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的最爱\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很美\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球上独有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's native only to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七个月后 橙色的花朵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}In seven months, the orange flowers
