Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咬上一囗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and then when you take a bite,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,种子会在你嘴里爆开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}the seeds just pop, pop, pop in your mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像装满果汁的小气球\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}like little balloons filled with juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还拿了这个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I also have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是某种游戏\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I think it's some kind of game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经有一个了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, you already have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你能教我吗  -可以\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Will you teach me? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但首先我希望你能帮我做件事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But first I'd like you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你告诉我 你离开这里后会发生什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I want you to tell me what happens when you leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有问题吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不知道能不能说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I... I don't know if I'm allowed to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定没关系的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, I'm sure it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有另一个房间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么样的房间  -一个大房间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What kind of room? - A big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你会怎么叫它\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I dunno what you'd call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是干什么的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What does this one do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样玩家就能对结果下赌注了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That allows the players to bet on the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And then what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掷骰子看谁先来吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We roll to see goes first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 房间外面是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, what's beyond the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有条走廊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, um, there's a hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-继续  -有很多扇门\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Go on. - There are many doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门后是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What's behind the doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能看\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not supposed to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁不让你看的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who told you not to look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个男人 我来掷\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The man. I'll roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲讲这个人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会喜欢他的 他人很好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You'd like him, he's very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是一直送你礼物的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's the one who's been sending you all the gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我讲讲这个男人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need you to tell me about the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我鼻子流血了  -我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- My nose is bleeding. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我他长什么样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不舒服\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't feel very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我他叫什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我好怕  -我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I'm scared. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人 他叫什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The man, his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}His name!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:03:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我他的名字\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你干什么呢  -训练\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What are you doing? - Training.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到士官长说的了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You heard what Chief said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还要这样多久\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How much longer are you gonna keep this up?
