Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以去找艾克森谈谈 花点时间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, you could talk to Ackerson, take some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-找个机会  -时间 干什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- get a chance to-- - Time, for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,治疗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多数时候我都不会注意到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't even notice it most days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都清楚才不是这样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, we both know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是斯巴达战士 凯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm a Spartan, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要去打仗的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把你植入物放回去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You can put your pellet back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有助于缓解疼痛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It will help with the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他们得先朝我开一枪\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They'll have to put a bullet in me first.
