Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉他们不信任我们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's like they don't trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咋了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有什么不对劲吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Think there's something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把科塔娜从你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's only been six months since...
