Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马吉 在圣所看到了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Makee, on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-马吉死了  -我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Makee's dead. - I know.
