Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要换\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why did you change that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得意思是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Uh, well, I think it means that--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还在外面呢 还没回来呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're still out there. They haven't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道的对吧  -钴队呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You know that, right? - Where's Cobalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我只是做本职工作而已  -出什么事了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Look, I'm just doing my job. - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我们也想知道呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, that's what we're trying to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队出什么事了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What happened to Cobalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 他们告诉我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have no idea. They tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来把牌子换了 所以我就过来换了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to change the board, so I, I change the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你来换的 凯斯 艾克森\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who tells you to change it? Keyes, Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换回去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Put that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱夫 我们找到一个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Clive, we've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 谢谢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ah, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个可不属于你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你属于我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But you belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟斯皮夫签过契约\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're indentured to the Spiffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么认为\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的标签可不是这么写的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, your tag says otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 站住\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下枪\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去小巷\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Take the alley!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住 她在这\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stop, she's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在那边 垃圾处理器 追\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's there. The disposal! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 听到没\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Shut up. Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去那边\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牲口\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放聪明点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Be a smart girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比·安买下了索伦的船员 他不会回来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ruby Ann bought Soren's crew. he's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克莱夫\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Clive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你个狡猾的贱人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You slippery bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜 现在我都不想速战速决了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's a shame. Now I won't even make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了停\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I said stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多严重\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这帮混蛋\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一辈子都在打仗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}At war your whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,崩溃的时候会意想不到的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}surprised when you break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-让我帮你  -这里不行\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Let me help. - Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以建议他们把你从前线撤下来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I could recommend that they pull your ass off the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以杀了你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I could kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才对嘛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放松 没人在看\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Relax, no one's looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How would you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-疼吗  -不疼\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- That hurt? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-和气些  -别让他们看到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Be nice. - Don't let them see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 有我在呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's cool, I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己不可能一辈子都这样的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know you can't do this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯巴达克战士永不死\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Spartans never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认真的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他事可以做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's other things to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他生活方式\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}other ways to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有考虑过这些吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You ever think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考虑什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Think about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不做斯巴达战士的人生\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Life without all this Spartan shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说活的庸庸碌碌\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You mean a life that doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 抱歉 我不是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Louis, I'm sorry, I didn't--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没事  -我不是说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- It's all right. - I didn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们这帮混蛋怎么想的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know how you assholes think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经也是你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I was you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前很优秀\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是最优秀的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You were the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别拍马屁了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't blow smoke up my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这还真是实话\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望你能跟我们一起作战\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I wish you were out there with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我以前也这么希望过\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, I used to wish that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就改想法了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会理解的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's Cobalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要喝一杯吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝酒\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那食物呢 你吃东西吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What about food? Do you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队出什么事了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What happened to Cobalt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还活着吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are they still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知 斯巴达战士是不会死的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, as far as I know, Spartans never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派我们出任务 要不然我就去找能派我们出去的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Clear us for action, or I'll find somebody who will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在威胁我要越级行事吗 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you threatening to go over my head, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢等级制度 我尊重这点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You like a hierarchy, I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但别搞错了 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But make no mistake here, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海军情报局才是主脑\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The ONI is running the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我就是海军情报局\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I am the ONI.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你确定不需要些什么吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You sure I can't get you something, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直说了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Then allow me to be direct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对圣所事件的描述已被证实是可疑的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your account of events on Sanctuary has proven dubious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法证实其真实性\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We were unable to corroborate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找那个下士 佩雷斯谈啊 她当时也在场\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, talk to that corporal, Perez, she was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我谈过 我们谈了很久\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, I did. We spoke at length,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你坚持发生的这些事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but these things that you insist happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟精英消灭了陆战队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Covenant Elites wiping out Marines?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些陆战队员死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Those Marines are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为他们是怎么死的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What do you think happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是星盟将星球玻璃化导致\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I think the Covenant glassed the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是场可怕的悲剧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I think it was a terrible tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事实是 那位下士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But the fact remains, the corporal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并没有证实你的说法\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}did not confirm your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这话什么意思\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是她完全不记得\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It means she has absolutely no recollection
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在圣所遇到的那些事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}of what you say you encountered on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在撒谎\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你设身处地为我想一下 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Put yourself in my position, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鉴于你最近的行为 你会相信你吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Given your recent behavior, would you trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有我们就赢不了这场战争 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Can't win this war without us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要个士官长 我们都需要\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need Master Chief. We all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但约翰 说到底\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But John, at the end of the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这身衣服换谁穿都行\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}he's just a guy in a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你带了吃的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I brought you food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉埃拉 你下来干什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Laera, what are you doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说了船准备好我会去找你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I told you I'd come get you when the ship was ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说今天就能准备好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You said it would be ready today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道我说了什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, I know what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们发现个问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Um... we found a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在流体系统管道中发现了个裂缝\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We found a crack in the stream manifold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-要多久  -那艘货船周围有很多碎片\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- How long? - There's a lot of debris around that cargo ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到的撞击比我们预想的要多\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}took more hits than we realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-多久  -很难讲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- How long? - It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几天吧 也许更久\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A couple of days, maybe more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们尽力了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're doing the best we can here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该上楼休息一下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You should go upstairs and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦绝不会丢下你们任何一个人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren never would've left any of you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那艘货船处于衰变轨道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That cargo ship was in a decaying orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被击中 失去了陀螺仪 要么分离 要么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We got hit, lost the gyro. It was either detach or--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-凯斯勒怎么样  -凯斯勒很好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- How's Kessler doing? - Kessler's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事对于孩子来说很难\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This sort of thing's pretty hard on a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-索伦没死  -当然没有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Soren is not dead. - No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着 明白吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's alive, do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉埃拉 我们都想找到索伦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Laera, we all wanna find Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道这不是碎石星唯一一艘飞船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know this isn't the only ship on the Rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是索伦的飞船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is Soren's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的舰长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你耳朵怎么回事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What happened to your ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是做错事了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 大人事小孩不懂\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, it's grown-up stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人事我懂的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know grown-up stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我得离开  -为什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I have to go. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 就是得走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Because... I just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏人在找你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Bad people are looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How do you--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了大人的事我懂的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I told you I know grown-up things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你什么都不知道  -你有危险\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You don't know anything. - You're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 你妈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You, your mom--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我爸回来 他就会保护我们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When my dad comes back, he'll protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他回不来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's not coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯勒\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-里兹 我看到你了  -靠\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz, I see you. - Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已确认目标身份 准备开火\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have PID on target, taking the shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说说 是什么感觉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me, what is it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -输的感觉 我不知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What? - Losing, I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你真烦人  -因为我没输过\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You're insufferable. - Because I've never lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是 知道了  -所以对我来说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Yeah, I get it. - So for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个全新的体验\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}it'll be a new experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-士官长 让他闭嘴吧  -再来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief, make him stop. - We're going again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-里兹 你上  -收到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Riz, you're up. - Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我可以继续 士官长  -我说了里兹来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Well, I can go, Chief. - I said Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-士官长  -干嘛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧她\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 还好吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, you good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想说的吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Something you wanna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-瓦纳克  -我来搞定\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Vannak. - I got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已确认目标身份\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have PID on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 加油啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不许放弃  -士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Don't you quit. - Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-起来  -我做不到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Get up! - I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再逼她了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You've gotta stop pushing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这训练一晚上了 为什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}we've been out here all night training, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们在训练\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Because they're training!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过我在圣所看到了什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I told you what I saw on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的敌人就在那里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Our enemy is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们越来越近了 我可以证明\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're getting close, I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.43,0:23:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么证明\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How are you gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找钴队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm gonna find Cobalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Run it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The game's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.17,0:23:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们要玩到50分\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But we're playing to 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.98,0:23:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经50多分了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I got over 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每轮骰子我都翻倍\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I turned the doubling cube each round,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.92,0:23:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每次都接受了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and you accepted every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.26,0:24:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候吃点小亏\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes taking a small loss
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比试图获胜要好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}is better than trying to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派你来的那个男人是谁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who's the man who sent you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.61,0:24:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道他的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How do you know about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.82,0:24:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些可爱的礼物\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, these lovely gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.46,0:24:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是有人给你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Someone must be giving them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.14,0:24:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流个不停呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.36,0:24:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说说那个男的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me about the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.35,0:24:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 你说过他人很好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, you said he's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.88,0:24:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 但描述一下他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, but describe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.12,0:24:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.26,0:24:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 我是做错什么了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What? Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.33,0:24:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我 看我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Look at me, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.26,0:24:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我好怕  -我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I'm scared. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.77,0:24:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我好害怕  -告诉我他叫什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I'm very scared. - Tell me his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.52,0:24:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我那个男人 他的名字\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me the man, his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.78,0:24:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么意义呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What's the point in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.95,0:25:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹 放松 没事的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz, relax. You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.92,0:25:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不该来这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.70,0:25:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是唯一一个能帮到你的人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's the only guy that can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.65,0:25:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.87,0:25:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他救过我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}'Cause he's the one who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.85,0:25:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我们从增强手术中出来的时候\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Look, when we came outta augmentation...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.10,0:25:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己焕然一新\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I felt completely new.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.53,0:25:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有人开始生病\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Even when people started getting sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.36,0:25:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是不可战胜的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I was invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.51,0:25:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几天后\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}After a couple of days,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.67,0:25:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我视野边缘出现一片黑暗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}there was this darkness at the edge of my vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.80,0:25:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我假装它不存在\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I just pretended like it wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.84,0:25:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但它蔓延\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But it grew...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.94,0:25:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越来越大\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and it grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.36,0:25:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我谁都没告诉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I never told anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.07,0:25:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本可以告诉我的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You could have told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.04,0:25:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不行  -为什么不行\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- No, I couldn't. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.02,0:25:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那样你就会知道我不是你们中的一员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}'Cause then you'd know I wasn't one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己只有几天时间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I knew I only had a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.31,0:25:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想当个瞎子\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't wanna be somebody going blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.51,0:26:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想当斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I wanted to be a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.11,0:26:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只那么一小会儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Even if just for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.20,0:26:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能看到东西的最后一天\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know, the last day I could really see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.10,0:26:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得看着你们所有人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I remember looking at all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.27,0:26:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是如此的骄傲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}how proud you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.50,0:26:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此的美丽\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}how beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.81,0:26:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后一切陷入黑暗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Then it all went dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.73,0:26:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.44,0:26:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.38,0:26:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个朋友\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.49,0:26:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊 朋友\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hello, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点担心约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I am a bit worried about John.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.85,0:26:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是士官长的能力 而是这个人市身\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not Master Chief, but John the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.29,0:26:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们共事很久\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I know how long you've been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.37,0:26:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道你在乎他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know you care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.91,0:27:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 我敢说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}In fact, I venture to say
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.82,0:27:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能比任何人都了解他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you probably know him better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.98,0:27:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-同意吗  -我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Do you agree? - Well, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.20,0:27:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也许你能帮我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I thought perhaps you might help me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.01,0:27:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.99,0:27:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that something you could do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.73,0:27:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.57,0:27:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到过任何行为迹象表明\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Have you witnessed any behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰可能会对他的团队构成威胁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that might indicate John could be a threat to his team...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.32,0:27:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可能对自己构成威胁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}or, God forbid, to himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.67,0:27:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.04,0:27:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就放心了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.54,0:27:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得太多了 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I just think it's a lot, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.86,0:27:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承载他所承载的 目睹他所目睹的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Carrying everything he carries, seeing everything he's seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.14,0:27:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他们对他做的那样 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Like what they did to him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.26,0:28:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有时候在想\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I just wonder sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.73,0:28:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能不能让过去成为过去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}if he can let the past become the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.25,0:28:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你担心约翰的精神状态吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you have concerns about John's mental state?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.21,0:28:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 绝对不是 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No. Absolutely not, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.71,0:28:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长很可靠 他是最好的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The chief is solid. He's the best we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.42,0:28:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相当理解他看上你什么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, I certainly understand what he sees in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.83,0:28:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.80,0:28:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只希望他重视你的忠诚\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I only hope he values your loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.07,0:28:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这些了吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Will that be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.99,0:28:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 解散\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.10,0:28:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的门永远为你敞开 凯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}My door is always open, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.49,0:28:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不告诉艾克森你看到了什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why didn't you tell Ackerson what you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.30,0:28:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 现在没空\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm sorry, this isn't a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.54,0:28:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.92,0:29:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祖母 回屋里去 好吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Abuela, just go back inside, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.56,0:29:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Everybody's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.24,0:29:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-这是谁啊  -他就要走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He was just about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.31,0:29:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很大只嘛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You are very large.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.73,0:29:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 女士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.97,0:29:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我同事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's someone I work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.16,0:29:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟塔莉亚都在那个星球上吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You were there on that planet with Talia?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.78,0:29:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.16,0:29:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还站外面干嘛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why are you standing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.24,0:29:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来一起呀\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come and join us,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.32,0:29:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在屋顶上准备了一大堆吃的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}we have a table full of food up on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.34,0:29:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一个来看我的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're not the first to come see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.05,0:29:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些战士以为伤疤只存在于外部\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You warriors think your scars are on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.35,0:29:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其实不是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.54,0:29:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.48,0:30:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.92,0:30:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是你的伤痛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's just your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.79,0:30:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.39,0:30:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让它走吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.83,0:30:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的人生是你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your life is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.97,0:30:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是属于你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.77,0:30:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I promise you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.25,0:30:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.58,0:31:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A ver,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.01,0:31:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招呼客人吃东西啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}make sure our guest gets enough to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.04,0:31:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你俩是什么情况\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What's the story with you two? Hmm? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.60,0:31:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能安静吃饭吗 拜托了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Can we just eat, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.83,0:31:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧这哥们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Look at this guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.35,0:31:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定特别招女人喜欢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}he must have women climbing all over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.05,0:31:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能是某些男人的菜哦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Probably some men too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.06,0:31:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 管好你自己\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, mind your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.31,0:31:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 塔莉亚以前没带过人回家\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on, Talia never brought anyone home before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.09,0:31:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是我带回来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't bring him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.21,0:31:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我觉得我们都应该知道他们有没有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, and I think we all deserve to know if they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.35,0:31:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼奥\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Antonio?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.44,0:31:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了 安东尼奥\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Basta, Antonio.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.99,0:31:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.27,0:31:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你的KDR是多少\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, what's your KDR?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.68,0:31:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,击毙和被击毙率\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kill-Death ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.91,0:31:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧兄弟 你不玩斯巴达进攻的吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on, man, you don't play Spartan Attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.45,0:31:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不记分的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't keep score.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.42,0:32:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差点吓尿裤子\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Think I almost peed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.63,0:32:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说了 他就是其中一员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I told you, he's one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.50,0:32:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打给贝托\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh! I'm calling Beto.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.67,0:32:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不行  -是 该打\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- No. - Yeah, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.91,0:32:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 家里有斯巴达战士来吃饭哎\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What? We have a Spartan at our table.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.97,0:32:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然得打给他了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Of course I'm gonna call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.62,0:32:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想致敬酒词\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'd like to make a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.72,0:32:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬塔莉亚和她的陆战队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To Talia and her Marines,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.44,0:32:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and the Spartans.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.30,0:32:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢他们的牺牲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We thank God for their sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.80,0:32:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬塔莉亚\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To Talia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.33,0:32:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-干杯  -塔莉亚\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Salud. - Talia.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.43,0:32:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小表妹狠狠教训了那帮星盟垃圾\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Little cousin who kicked some serious Covenant ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.76,0:32:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你怎么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, what's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.48,0:32:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 混蛋\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Way to go, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.41,0:32:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我干什么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.92,0:32:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中继站附近通讯中断\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The comms went down around the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.54,0:32:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是什么原因造成的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I couldn't figure out what was causing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.06,0:33:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时在扫描波段 然后\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I was scanning the band and...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.76,0:33:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就听到了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I heard something...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.42,0:33:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干扰里有声音\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}in the interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.80,0:33:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到什么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.10,0:33:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.42,0:33:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道还有别人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I just knew we weren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.31,0:33:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道外面有东西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I knew there was something out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.02,0:33:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I could feel it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.01,0:33:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰德也能感觉到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and Rand could feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.67,0:33:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都看不到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.45,0:33:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我战友都牺牲了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And now all my guys are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.57,0:33:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么解释\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.31,0:33:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么解释为什么那东西没杀我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How do you explain why that thing didn't kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.23,0:33:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它本该也把我杀了的啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}'Cause it should've killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.11,0:33:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我没告诉艾克森的原因\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's why I didn't tell Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.31,0:34:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们授予我勋章\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They gave me a medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.76,0:34:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不知道由头是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I still don't know what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.65,0:34:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为活下来吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Surviving?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.13,0:34:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是活下来了而已\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is that all I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.64,0:34:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.61,0:34:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了一条信息 这种情况还会再次发生\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You heard a message. This will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.04,0:34:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每天都会想起这事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You'll think about it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.95,0:34:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的脸会在你最意想不到的时候蹦出来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Their faces pop up when you least expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.43,0:34:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会好转\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Doesn't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.34,0:34:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只会渐行渐远\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just gets further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.18,0:35:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.82,0:35:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克隆人都说是个很好的男人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The clones all described a nice man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.71,0:35:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你却站在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And yet here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.37,0:35:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都清楚终有一天我会来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, we both knew I'd be here someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.11,0:35:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲在弗农港的花园里有棵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There was a pomegranate tree in my father's garden
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.53,0:35:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石榴树\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}in Port Vernon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.77,0:35:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他花了数年时间培育它\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He spent years cultivating it,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.47,0:35:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管那棵树并不是安迪密安星球的本土植物\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}even though they're not native to Endymion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.60,0:35:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾经每天都在日出前几小时\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And he used to wake me up a couple of hours
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.57,0:35:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫醒我去打理花园\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}before sunrise every day to till the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.19,0:35:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为此怨恨过他 觉得这份工作有失我身份\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I resented him for this, I thought the work was beneath me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.41,0:35:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得有天晚上 有场雷雨\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I remember one evening there was a lightning storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.04,0:35:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我偷溜出房间 把他的树点着了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and I snuck out of my room, and I set his tree on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.77,0:36:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他从没怀疑过我跟这件事有关系\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He never suspected I had anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.59,0:36:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没告诉过任何人这个故事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have never told anyone that story...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.41,0:36:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而不知怎么的 那棵树\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and yet somehow that tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.27,0:36:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个人知道这件事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's only one person who could know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.77,0:36:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证 如有雷同纯属巧合\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I assure you, any resemblance is pure coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.19,0:36:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.81,0:36:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-科塔娜吗 她很安全  -约翰在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Cortana? She's secure. - Where's John?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.10,0:36:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不要操之过急\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let's not get ahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.61,0:36:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想从我这里得到什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is it you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.80,0:36:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想给你介绍个人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What I want is to introduce you to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.41,0:36:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是朱莉娅\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.26,0:36:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她将是你的随从\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She'll be your attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.65,0:36:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你们二位会很高兴认识对方的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm sure you two will enjoy getting to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.04,0:36:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的树\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.60,0:37:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我看钴队任务的飞行计划\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Show me the flight plan for Cobalt team's mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.11,0:37:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有与该呼号相关的任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No missions associated with that call sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.75,0:37:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我看所有斯巴达的飞行计划\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Show me all Spartan flight plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.30,0:37:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显示斯巴达飞行计划\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Displaying Spartan flight plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.84,0:38:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 科塔娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hello, Cortana.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.99,0:38:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 艾克森上校\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hello, Colonel Ackerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.52,0:38:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你提供的信息有用吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you find the information I provided useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.63,0:38:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相当有用 谢谢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Quite, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.84,0:38:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于哈尔西博士 你还有什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is there anything else you would like to know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.44,0:38:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想了解的吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}about Dr. Halsey?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.29,0:38:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没了 可以以后再说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, we can save that for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.52,0:38:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你的问题有什么进展吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So, have you made any progress with the problem I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.90,0:38:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的 但这个模拟很复杂\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, but it's a complex simulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.26,0:38:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能让我访问外部系统\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I could provide you with a more accurate analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.58,0:38:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能给你更准确的分析\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}if you could give me access to external systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.83,0:38:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不行\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.33,0:38:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你尽最大努力\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Oh. - But give it your best shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.26,0:38:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有误差裕度\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}even with a margin for error,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.82,0:38:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的预测还是有价值的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}there's value to your projections.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.25,0:38:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据我掌握的数据\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Based on the data available to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.16,0:38:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能性为97%\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}there's a 97% probability.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.87,0:38:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据你所得到的数据\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And with the data you've been given,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.46,0:38:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么可行的策略\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}are there any viable strategies you would recommend
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.96,0:39:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以防止这种结果\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to prevent that outcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.99,0:39:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管采取什么行动\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}All of my simulations return the same result
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.32,0:39:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所有模拟结果都是一样的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}regardless of any action taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.35,0:39:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.13,0:39:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没什么可做的了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So there's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.22,0:39:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以继续模拟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can continue to run simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.41,0:39:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.73,0:39:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要走了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.21,0:39:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.28,0:39:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽可能再来看你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll try and visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.36,0:39:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.40,0:39:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没办法来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.43,0:39:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据模拟结果\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}According to the simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.24,0:39:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.29,0:39:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是人类会这么说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's just something people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.31,0:39:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交叉搜索通讯中继站\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Crosscheck communications relays.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.89,0:39:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有两个正在执行的任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There are two active missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子午线中继站 标准船员轮换\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Meridian relay, standard crew rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.34,0:39:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未知任务   埃里丹星系\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Unknown mission, Epsilon Eridane system.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.89,0:40:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放大\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Zoom in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.81,0:40:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务时间 81小时\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Mission time, 81 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.26,0:40:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-识别呼号  -无呼号\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Identify call sign. - No call sign
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.49,0:40:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与此飞行计划关联\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}associated with this flight plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.93,0:40:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就没离开过那个星球\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They never left the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.14,0:40:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HV32 这里是致远星飞行B队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hotel Victor 3-2, this is Reach Flight Bravo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.07,0:40:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被批准进入长角牛空域 航向249\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You are cleared for Sector Longhorn, heading 2-4-9'er.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.52,0:40:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到 B队 32退出\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Copy that, Bravo. 3-2 out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.26,0:40:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自动驾驶解除 新航线\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Autopilot disengaged, new course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.31,0:40:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不是训练吗  -怎么回事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- No training? - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.48,0:40:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是要去长角牛谷吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I thought we were going to Longhorn Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.42,0:40:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还挺期待把你们打的落花流水的呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I was looking forward to turning you all into chump bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.00,0:40:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-计划有变  -什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Change of plans. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.91,0:40:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我们要去哪儿  -韦谢格勒中继站 里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Where are we going? - Visegrad Relay. Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.03,0:40:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在星盟发动攻击之前\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The comms array on Sanctuary went down
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.95,0:40:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣所的通讯中继器失灵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}just before the Covenant attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.41,0:41:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦谢格勒几天前断联 他们派钴队去了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Visegrad went down a few days ago, and they sent Cobalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.26,0:41:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去把他们找回来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're going to get 'em back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.56,0:41:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们可以作战了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So we're cleared for combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.21,0:41:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 小维 准备好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Affirmative. Vic, ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.33,0:41:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦纳克 搭建主要通信接囗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Vannak, conduct PCIs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.88,0:41:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You got it, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.56,0:41:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务具体内容是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What exactly is the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.10,0:41:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在致远星的星盟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant's on Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.64,0:41:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扛住\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.71,0:41:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Make ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.24,0:41:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.54,0:41:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳住\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.11,0:42:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停火 停火\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cease fire! Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.61,0:42:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停火\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.01,0:42:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.24,0:42:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}First squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.84,0:42:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放松\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.33,0:42:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一队 报告情况\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}First squad, sit-rep!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.43,0:42:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二队 出发\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Second squad, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.57,0:42:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交火\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Covenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.06,0:43:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.14,0:43:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗不公平\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's no honor in this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.46,0:43:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门.\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Door.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.74,0:43:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Please.


